text: Prhajevo () is a small settlement northwest of Velike Lašče in central Slovenia. The entire Municipality of Velike Lašče lies in the traditional region of Lower Carniola. It is included in the Central Slovenia Statistical Region.Velike Lašče municipal site ==References== ==External links== *Prhajevo on Geopedia Category:Populated places in the Municipality of Velike Lašče
